events.name: Future Fridays: What's in Your Backpack?
events.description:
Think you left civics education behind when you graduated from school? Join us for our 2nd experiment in civics education for adults where we will explore the the privilege that we encounter in our lives. What is in our invisible backpack? How can we create more equality? Should we create more equality?  

This session is brought to us by Friends of Future Fridays: Cheryl, Eddie and Winnie.

== 
We are keeping this session small -- please email chewlin.kay@sl2square.org asap to register!
events.location: Lee Kuan Yew School of Public Policy, 469C Bukit Timah Road, Singapore 259772
